                  <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                      The RYA Coastal Skipper/Yachtmaster theory course is an advanced course that builds on the knowledge gained on the <a href="/courses/rya-day-skipper-theory"><em>shorebased Day Skipper course</em></a>. It is aimed at sailors and motor boaters who are looking to undertake more complex passages perhaps offshore or at night.
